{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":527266,"duration_api_ms":494530,"num_turns":103,"result":"\nThe fix is complete. Let me provide a summary of the changes made:\n\n## Summary\n\nThe fix adapts modin 0.25.0 to pandas 2.1.2 by updating the deprecation warning message for the `pct_change` method's `fill_method` and `limit` parameters.\n\n### Changes Made:\n\n1. **`modin/pandas/base.py`** (line 2191):\n   - Changed the condition from `if fill_method is not lib.no_default or limit is not lib.no_default:` to `if fill_method not in (lib.no_default, None) or limit is not lib.no_default:`\n   - Updated the warning message to match pandas 2.1.2: `\"The 'fill_method' keyword being not None and the 'limit' keyword in ... are deprecated ...\"`\n\n2. **`modin/pandas/groupby.py`** (line 562):\n   - Applied the same changes to the `DataFrameGroupBy.pct_change` method\n\n3. **`modin/pandas/test/test_groupby.py`**:\n   - Updated the filterwarning marker (line 79-81) to match the new warning message\n   - Updated the test `test_groupby_pct_change_parameters_warning` (line 3065-3074) to match the new warning message\n\n### Root Cause:\nIn pandas 2.1.2, the deprecation warning for `pct_change` changed its condition (now only triggers when `fill_method` is not `None`) and the warning message text was updated. The old modin code was using the old warning message, which caused test failures due to:\n1. Filterwarnings not matching the new message\n2. Explicit tests checking for the old warning message","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"10e1c01e-8404-4772-b881-3719910af6b0","total_cost_usd":10.432674749999997,"usage":{"input_tokens":3151624,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2171,"cache_read_input_tokens":388320,"output_tokens":22117,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"cache_deleted_input_tokens":0,"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed":{"inputTokens":3318866,"outputTokens":23189,"cacheReadInputTokens":400335,"cacheCreationInputTokens":2171,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":10.432674749999997,"contextWindow":196000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"25c120c2-8394-484a-b376-712676d1cbe0"}
